{"tid":1180251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港股五窮月冧2800點　差絕全球","createTime":"2019-05-31T16:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T13:37:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9e515ab9999bd55e5f8d384795868c691aa1f5","tid":1180251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"中美貿易關係急速惡化，5月份環球股市顯著受壓，當中又以港股「最傷」。5月份恒生指數累挫2,798點，以點數計為史上最慘「五窮月」，累積跌幅達到9.42%，衰絕環球主要股市，港股市值單月蒸發超過3.3萬億元。<br />\n<br />\n統計顯示，5月份及6月份港股走勢關連度高，過去10年同步比率達80%，反映「六絕月」港股仍高危。事實上，綜合多名證券分析員及基金經理意見意見，普遍預期6月份港股會續尋底，若中美貿易形勢沒有起色，恒指恐跌至25,500到26,000點始喘穩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190601/bkn-20190601001526256-0601_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190601%2Fbkn-20190601001526256-0601_00842_001.html&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=6ea8ae6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190601/bkn-20190601001526256-0601_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"352fcc899d37fb1add42def6b4316066db9a67fc","tid":1180251,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca0eb5288967d18a4bd0b1372c63d6baecb2266","tid":1180251,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"7月入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d96a6db1f80d07dd347b7633e0792632173435","tid":1180251,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ca0eb5288967d18a4bd0b1372c63d6baecb2266","tid":1180251,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"7月入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"可能香港已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 